title: 2020 CFB Pick Em Week 2 (Week 1 Didn't Exist)
description:
We're back for whatever this football season even is. We start with some housecleaning to start week 8. The Squeeze Out is over, maybe. Rico creates the competition for the full year and gives a great gift to the guys. Week 2 slate and mortal locks of the week!
